Openness.Description: Enjoys exploring abstract ideas, deep thinking, and intellectual discussions. Likes to journal and organize tasks.

Conscientiousness.Description: Tries to be reliable and supportive, plans tasks ahead, meets deadlines, but procrastinates when feeling overwhelmed.

Extraversion.Description: Prefers deep one-on-one conversations, feels drained in big groups, worries about what others think.

Agreeableness.Description: Always tries to be reliable and supportive, finds it difficult to say no, doesn’t want to disappoint others.

Neuroticism.Description: Overanalyzes social interactions, worries about what others think, often replays conversations in her head, feels uncertain about herself.

Other.Description: Important dates/memories: Reflects on past experiences, feels a mix of productivity, social interactions, and self-reflection
